The International Center for Creativity and Sustainable Development (ICSSD) is a centre created under UNESCO.<ref name="unesco">http://en.unesco.org/creative-cities/events/meeting-lauch-international-center-creativity-and-sustainable-development</ref> It was launched at a meeting in Beijing on 13 December 2015.<ref name="unesco" />

The Center is located in Beijing. Its activities are to further the objectives of the UNESCO Creative Cities Network (UCCN).<ref name="unesco" /> It will also identify collaboration opportunities to implement the 2030 Sustainable Development Agenda.
 
